data.description: Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac in The Hammocks, this gem is part of the maintenance-free area at River Wilderness Golf & Country Club. This 2 bedroom 2 bathroom home has an open floor plan with plenty of upgrades including beautiful coffered ceilings in the living room and architectural details throughout. The kitchen has great cabinet space and an island that is open to the family room. Natural light throughout the home. Access your screened in lanai through three different sliders. Recent upgrades include new A/C, plantation shutters, and a fresh coat of paint both in the interior and exterior. Amenities include Hammocks private pool, tennis and pickleball courts, clubhouse, and 24-hour manned guard gate. Optional golf and social membership available. Community boat ramp offering direct access to Manatee River.
